### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json
@token = your-jwt-token-here

### Get AI-Powered Recommendations (requires authentication and some rated movies)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recommendations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Genre-Based Recommendations - Action
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recommendations/genre/action

### Get Genre-Based Recommendations - Sci-Fi
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recommendations/genre/sci-fi

### Get Genre-Based Recommendations - Drama
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recommendations/genre/drama

### Get Genre-Based Recommendations - Crime
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recommendations/genre/crime

### Get Genre-Based Recommendations - Adventure
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recommendations/genre/adventure

### Get Genre-Based Recommendations - Romance
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recommendations/genre/romance

### Get Genre-Based Recommendations - Fantasy
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recommendations/genre/fantasy